TI  - Developing natural resources database with Nigeriasat-1 satellite data and geographical information systems
T2  - EGYPTIAN JOURNAL OF REMOTE SENSING AND SPACE SCIENCES
LA  - English
KW  - Database
KW  - Geographical information systems
