TI  - Build Collaborative Models or Capacity? Comparison of Techniques for Building Bayesian Networks for the Natural Resource Management Regions of Australia
T2  - MODSIM 2007: INTERNATIONAL CONGRESS ON MODELLING AND SIMULATION: LAND, WATER AND ENVIRONMENTAL MANAGEMENT: INTEGRATED SYSTEMS FOR SUSTAINABILITY
