TI  - Temporal and spatial simulation of vegetation dynamics in a Mediterranean protected mountain area under different farming management scenarios
T2  - ANIMAL FARMING AND ENVIRONMENTAL INTERACTIONS IN THE MEDITERRANEAN REGION
