TI  - Constraint-based systematic conservation planning: a generic and expressive approach applied to decision support for the conservation of New Caledonian forests
T2  - BOIS ET FORETS DES TROPIQUES
LA  - French
KW  - systematic conservation planning
KW  - decision support
KW  - forest conservation
