AB  - The conservation of water resources deals with spatial plans, influencing territorial management tools at regional and local scale. This paper aimed to analyze the planning tools applied in Brazil, focusing on the Northern Coast of Sao Paulo. The methodology was based on the analysis on the articulation of laws: Politica Nacional de Recursos Hidricos, Estatuto da Cidade, Plano de Bacia Hidrografica, Zoneamento Ecologico-Economico and Plano Diretor Municipal. As results, there are troubles in the laws interaction's, with lack of decision support.
