AB  - Bridge's digital simulation management and conservation technology is the most important technology of the intelligent and informationization of the bridge's management and conservation. It can overcome many drawbacks of the early artificial bridge's management and conservation, such as low degree of automation, pool data processing ability and heavy workload. It can also provide decision support based on the data collected by people and the health monitoring automation system. At the same time, three-dimensional simulation of the bridge makes the situation of bridge's health more intuitive and visual. This technology help us control the situation of bridge's health more effectively, discover and repair defects promptly, ensure the safety of the bridge, and provide some artificial checking index data for comprehensive assessment of bridge condition. Based on a digital simulation management and conservation system of a bridge, this paper will introduce the key technology used in the system.
