AB  - South-to-North Water Transfer Project is a significant project of benefiting the nation, which is optimization and dispatch on water source. Danjiangkou Reservoir is the water source of South-to-North Water Transfer Project, which is in charge of the success of water quality. This paper discusses the main work of Danjiangkou basin management on valley soil and water conservation, non-point source pollution controlling, Water-Level-Fluctuation Zone exploitation and utilization, valley and water function planning, water resource management and reservoir operation, ecology compensation mechanism completion. Danjiangkou basin management depends on modern technology. In order to improve the management efficiency, it is important to innovate the methods of basin management. Remote sense and GIS technology application, network and Communication technology, informatization and decision support system are expected to apply in basin management field.
