AB  - The multi-energy complemental'', system is one of the important ways to alleviate the environmental and energy consumption problems by coupling cold, heat, electrical and multiple energy sources. However, due to the internal complexity of the system, there are multiple coupling methods and different coupling methods, so the comprehensive benefits of different scenarios are different. Therefore, we construct an evaluation index system and a comprehensive evaluation model for the operating benefits of the multi-energy complementary system from economy, environment, society and energy conservation, We combined optimization examples to analyze the optimal operation plan of the multi-energy complementary system under different application scenarios, and verified the feasibility and effectiveness of the comprehensive evaluation modd. This provides effective decision support for the sustainable development of the multi-energy complementary system.
